overview: Gitta, Agnes, Angel, and Nando are members of a band led by Popo. When Gitta quits the band, Popo offers the vocalist position to Gaby. Then Gaby and Popo fall in love but Gitta unexpectedly reappears. Gitta breaks the news to Gaby that Popo is her ex-boyfriend. This unsettles Gaby especially when Popo treats Gitta with great concern when she has an accident. Then Nando suggests that they participate in a band competition to secure a recording contract. But the competition becomes very fierce and dirty tricks start being used.
title: Gaby dan Lagunya
